channel.title: Script to cut any log I say then burn it (or bank it if u can) :)
channel.description: i want a universal script that it can cut any log anywhere i say then burn it (or if possible, bank it) it don't have to bank, but it would be nice if it could. also in the script it has colors/names written down so in setup i can type in log, yew log, willow log, oak log, etc. and have randoms, and anitrandom events, so i can not get one of those stupid multiplying boxes (omg i hate those once i had 2000 of those in my inventory and had to get rid of my rs name :mad: ) so if u get this, email it to me at hy71194-at-gmail.com (replase -at- with @), and post it here :) if you can do this for me, thank you, thank you, thank you, thank you, thank you, thank you, thank you, thank you, thank you, thank you! lol

item.dc:creator: @MastrChief MastrChief
item.description:
@MastrChief wrote:

Sorry to bump an old topic, but I would just like to confirm that at one point, the boxes were stackable, and if you tried to bank them, they would duplicate with each click, filling up all the space in your inventory, and then starting ‘layers’.

They changed it in one of they’re updates due to the major hassle of solving all those boxes.
